1
00:00:14,240 --> 00:00:17,320
새벽 네 시 모니터 하나 켜놓고
At four AM, with one monitor on,

2
00:00:17,320 --> 00:00:19,620
줄줄이 코드를 써 내려가
Writing line after line of code.

3
00:00:19,620 --> 00:00:23,339
에러 백 개쯤 지우고 나면
After deleting about a hundred errors,

4
00:00:23,339 --> 00:00:26,320
캐릭터 하나가 눈을 떠
One character opens its eyes.

5
00:00:26,320 --> 00:00:30,719
아무도 모르는 이 작은 세계
This small world, unknown to anyone,

6
00:00:30,719 --> 00:00:33,460
내 손끝에서 태어나는 중
Is being born from my fingertips.

7
00:00:33,460 --> 00:00:37,479
픽셀 속의 꿈을 만들어가
Creating a dream within the pixels,

8
00:00:37,479 --> 00:00:40,259
한 칸 한 칸 점프해 올라가
Jumping up one space at a time.

9
00:00:40,259 --> 00:00:44,359
버그투성이 밤을 건너서
Crossing over a bug-ridden night,

10
00:00:44,359 --> 00:00:46,920
나만의 게임이 시작돼
My own game begins.

11
00:00:55,619 --> 00:01:19,319
완성 버튼을 누르는 그날
The day I press the 'complete' button,

12
00:01:19,319 --> 00:01:22,040
온 세상이 플레이하게 될 거야
The whole world will get to play it.

13
